  <body>
    <header>
      <para style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height:2.0;"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Trunc</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Trunc</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">(Value) truncates Value to an integer by rounding it towards zero.  If the number being truncated is outside the range -(2</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:8pt; vertical-align:super;" translate="true">31</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">-1) and +(2</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-size:8pt; vertical-align:super;" translate="true">31</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">-1), the function will return whichever of those numbers is closest. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">See also </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Round" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Round</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
  </body>
